data.description:
You've got yourself a night club. Now you need a bouncer. Why not build one? Make a bouncer with a method that accepts list of people (name, age) and returns filtered list of people that can enter the club. Age should be equal or above bouncers's age limit or name should be on guest list to enter the club. When constructing the bouncer, pass age limit and guest list.

Notes:
Guest names search should be case insensitive.

Assume guest has valid name - string.
Assume guest has valid age - number.
Assume guest list is always passed to bouncer in constructor.
Assume min age is always passed to bouncer as a number.

```
function Bouncer(settings) {
